preferences: learn more about AI Engineer role

key_facts: AI Engineers are responsible for turning AI models into practical systems
They don't always use deep learning, but choose algorithms based on problem, data, and system requirements
They start projects from understanding business or product problems, then defining necessary data, evaluating data quality, suggesting modeling approaches, and building pipelines
AI Engineers work with Product Managers, Data Engineers, Backend Engineers, DevOps/Cloud Engineers
